    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ASR Outdoor 260lb HMPE survival cord is widely used for military, marine, sporting goods and aerospace applications. It has a high tensile strength and rated at a 200lbs breaking strength. ASR Outdoor HMPE specialty cordage is a very durable cord for use in extreme conditions, made from braided high molecular polyethylene material. It is lightweight, has a low-stretch and UV resistant making it ideal for survival kits, bug out bags, emergency use and everyday edc situations. ASR Outdoor survival cord can be rapidly deployed when compared to tradition 550 paracord and is significantly smaller and lighter - while still being strong enough to count on in an emergency</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor HMPE 260LB Utility Cord, Black Multipurpose Braided Line Many Length</h2>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor 260lb HMPE survival cord is widely used for military, marine, sporting goods and aerospace applications. It has a high tensile strength and rated at a 200lbs breaking strength.</p>\n  <p>ASR Outdoor HMPE specialty cordage is a very durable cord for use in extreme conditions, made from braided high molecular polyethylene material. It is lightweight, has a low-stretch and UV resistant making it ideal for survival kits, bug out bags, emergency use and everyday edc situations. ASR Outdoor survival cord can be rapidly deployed when compared to tradition 550 paracord and is significantly smaller and lighter - while still being strong enough to count on in an emergency.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>HMPE CORD LINE:</strong> Tensile Strength: 266lbs; Diameter: .03&quot; (VERY THIN); Braided from 3 strands of high molecular polyethylene</li>\n    <li><strong>ENHANCED COMPOSITION:</strong> Polymer abrasion resistant coating impregnated into the braid for added abrasion, corrosion and UV resistance. Low stretch, floats and can not be seen on night vision</li>\n    <li><strong>Lengths Available:</strong> 25, 50, 100, 500, 1000 feet; Color: Black; Breaking Strength: 260LB</li>\n    <li>Ideal for survival and emergency kits, perimeter trip wire alarm, bug out bag, EDC, wildlife mitigation, craft and hobby</li>\n    <li>Made in the USA</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/camping_outdoors/cord/HMPE Kevlar Utility Cord Main.jpg\" alt=\"The ASR Outdoor 260lb HMPE survival cord is widely used for military, marine, sporting goods and aerospace applications\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> KSC-1K-949</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 781142046889</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Black</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor utility cord is made in the USA; constructed from 3 strands of HMPE thread braided together and coated in a proprietary protective coating giving added abrasion and UV resistance. ASR Outdoor cord is heat-resistant, allowing it to be used as a cutting tool for sawing wood, ropes, flex-cuffs while functioning as a perimeter trip line that will not be seen on night vision goggles.</p>\n  <p>Weighing less than a few ounces, the survival cord is optimal for building emergency shelters, repairing your gear, trip wire, traps, bows, and snares. This cord is the perfect companion to every emergency kit and ideal for every day carry, edc.</p>\n  <p>Available in multiple lengths. Colors available: Black</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The ASR Outdoor 260lb HMPE survival cord is widely used for military, marine, sporting goods and aerospace applications. It has a high tensile strength and rated at a 200lbs breaking strength. ASR Outdoor HMPE specialty cordage is a very durable cord for use in extreme conditions, made from braided high molecular polyethylene material. It is lightweight, has a low-stretch and UV resistant making it ideal for survival kits, bug out bags, emergency use and everyday edc situations. ASR Outdoor survival cord can be rapidly deployed when compared to tradition 550 paracord and is significantly smaller and lighter - while still being strong enough to count on in an emergency.",
